cs.AI, cs.IT, cs.DB, cs.SY, cs.SE 

The paper discusses the use of autonomous agents to encode the semantics of observers into a description of spacetime. This involves the unification of real and artificial spaces, such as databases and information webs, with natural spacetime. Therefore, the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Information Theory (cs.IT), Databases (cs.DB), Systems and Control (cs.SY), and Software Engineering (cs.SE).
